"description" = "Track Berlin public transport in real time — see U-Bahn, S-Bahn, trams, and buses move live across the city.\n\nBerlin Transit Map shows exactly where your next ride is, updated continuously with official BVG data.\n\nLIVE VEHICLE TRACKING\n• Watch vehicles move in real time on the map\n• Color-coded lines for every transit type\n• Tap any vehicle for route and delay details\n\nALL TRANSIT TYPES\n• U-Bahn (Metro)\n• S-Bahn (City Rail)\n• Tram\n• Bus\n• Regional trains\n\nREAL-TIME DEPARTURES\n• Live departure boards for every stop\n• Delay alerts so you're never caught off guard\n• Arrival countdowns updated continuously\n\nMODERN DESIGN\n• Clean, native map interface\n• Smooth animations and intuitive controls\n• Dark mode support\n• Optimized for Mac and large screens\n\nPRIVACY FOCUSED\n• No account required\n• No personal data collected\n• No location tracking\n\nPERFECT FOR\n• Daily commuters in Berlin\n• Tourists exploring the city\n• Transit enthusiasts\n• Planning your next journey\n\nDownload Berlin Transit Map for faster decisions, fewer surprises, and better timing — every day.";
